column16: Manny Machado flies out to right fielder Jose Bautista.
Nick Markakis doubles (11) on a line drive to center fielder Colby Rasmus.   Danny Valencia scores.    Steve Pearce scores.    Yamaico Navarro scores.
Yamaico Navarro singles on a line drive to left fielder Melky Cabrera.   Danny Valencia to 3rd.    Steve Pearce to 2nd.
Danny Valencia doubles (2) on a line drive to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
Matt Wieters grounds into a double play, shortstop Munenori Kawasaki to second baseman Emilio Bonifacio to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.   Chris Davis out at 2nd.
Chris Davis singles on a line drive to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
Adam Jones grounds out, third baseman Brett Lawrie to first baseman Edwin Encarnacion.
J.   Hardy homers (9) on a fly ball to left field.   Nick Markakis scores.    Manny Machado scores.
Manny Machado singles on a line drive to right fielder Jose Bautista.   Nick Markakis to 2nd.
Nick Markakis singles on a ground ball to left fielder Melky Cabrera.
